\id COL ‑ Ikizu Colossians 
\h Abhakorosaayi 
\toc3 Abhakorosaayi 
\toc2 Abhakorosaayi 
\toc1 Ɨnyarʉbha ya Paaurʉ kwa Abhakorosaayi 
\mt2 Ɨnyarʉbha ya Paaurʉ kwa 
\mt1 Abhakorosaayi 
\imt1 Ʉbhʉkangati 
\ip Ɨnyarʉbha yɨnʉ yandikirwɨ na Paaurʉ, umutumwa wa Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ, kwa Abhakiriisitʉ bhʉ ʉrʉbhɨri rwa Korosaayi. Korosaayi rwarɨ ʉrʉbhɨri rusuuhu mʉrʉbhɨri rwa Asiya. Sikʉ zɨnʉ Asiya ni‑Bhuturuki. 
\ip Paaurʉ akaandɨka ɨnyarʉbha yɨnʉ hanʉ aarɨ mokebhoho. Ewe ataarɨ agiirɨ Korosaayi, nawe akiigwa kʉbha abhiija bhʉ ʉrʉrɨmɨ bhaarɨ bharanyaacha abhaatʉ iyo. Abhakiriisitʉ bha Korosaayi bhaarɨ amaribhita abhɨrɨ, Abhakiriisitʉ bhɨ Ɨkɨyaahudi na bhi Ikigiriki. 
\ip Kwarɨ na Abhayaahudi abhandɨ bhanʉ bhiijiryɨ amiija gʉ ʉrʉrɨmɨ, bhaarɨ bhariija kʉbha nangabha ʉmʉʉtʉ aarɨ mʉhɨmba wa Yɨɨsu, ataaturirɨ kwisiriribhwa na Mungu arɨɨbhɨ ataasaarirwɨ na ataatunirɨ imigirʉ na amanarʉ gɨ Ɨkɨyaahudi. Kwarɨ na Abhagiriki bhanʉ bhiijiryɨ amiija gʉ ʉrʉrɨmɨ, bhaarɨ bhariija kʉbha, kʉ kʉbha ʉmʉʉtʉ arakora ʉbhʉbhɨ na Mungu ataana ʉbhʉbhɨ, ɨtaarɨ ɨratʉrɨkana Yɨɨsu abhɨ Mungu na iikarɨ kʉʉsɨ nchʉ ʉmʉʉtʉ. 
\ip Paaurʉ aragarukirya amiija gʉ ʉrʉrɨmɨ gayo kwa kʉgamba amaheene igʉrʉ wa Yɨɨsu. Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ ni‑Mungu, nɨ‑Mʉkʉrʉ wa bhyʉsi kʉʉsɨ na kwisaarʉ. Akiikara kʉʉsɨ, aarɨ ʉmʉʉtʉ, na akakwa igʉrʉ wʉ ʉbhʉbhɨ bhwɨtʉ korereke tobheererwe. Ʉmʉʉtʉ ariimwisiriryɨ, kʉtakʉbhaho ubhwɨndi bhwu ukutuna simʉka yʉyʉʉsi. 
\ip Paaurʉ arabhabhʉʉrɨra Abhakiriisitʉ, ereenderwa bhatigɨ zeteemwa zɨmbɨ zɨ ɨkarɨ, na bhiikarɨ ubhwikari ubhuhya bhʉnʉ bhokozomera Mungu. 
\c 1  
\s1 Amakeerenʼya 
\p  
\v 1 Ɨnyarʉbha yɨnʉ nandikirɨ inyɨ Paaurʉ, umutumwa\f + \fr 1:1 \fk Umutumwa\ft . Kʉmaragɨrɨra bhʉkʉngʼu, rora ringʼana \ft \+it abhatumwa\+it* muKiniibhasa.\f* wa Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ kʉbhʉsɨɨgi bhwa Mungu, nɨrɨ hamwɨmwɨ na Timoseo, umwisirirya ʉmʉkɨndichɨtʉ.  
\v 2 Tʉrabhaandɨkɨra imwɨ abharɨndu\f + \fr 1:2 \fk Abharɨndu\ft . Kʉmaragɨrɨra bhʉkʉngʼu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* bha Mungu bhanʉ mukwikara mʉrʉbhɨri rwa Korosaayi, imwɨ abhahiiri bhɨɨtʉ abharonge ku ukugwatana na Kiriisitʉ. 
\p Ɨbhɨgʉngi no omorembe kurwa kwa Bhaabha Mungu, bhɨbhɨ na niimwɨ. 
\s1 Amasabhi nu ubhukumya kwa Mungu 
\p  
\v 3 Hanʉ tʉkʉbhasabhɨra, tʉrakumya Mungu ibhaga ryʉsi, Wiisɨ wʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ wɨɨtʉ Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ.  
\v 4 Tʉrakorabhu, kʉ kʉbha twigwirɨ igʉrʉ wu ubhwisirirya bhwanyu kwa Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ ni igʉrʉ wʉ ʉbhʉsɨɨgi bhʉnʉ mʉnabhwɨ abharɨndu bhʉʉsi bha Mungu.  
\v 5 Ubhwisirirya bhwanyu nʉ ʉbhʉsɨɨgi bhwanyu bhʉkarwɨra kubhwisɨgi bhʉnʉ Mungu abhatɨɨrɨɨrɨ mwisaarʉ. Mukiigwa igʉrʉ wu ubhwisɨgi bhuyo, hanʉ mwarwaziirwɨ amangʼana ga amaheene gɨ Ɨngʼana Ɨnzʉmu.  
\v 6 Ɨngʼana Ɨnzʉmu yɨnʉ yaahikirɨ kwa niimwɨ, ɨranyaragana mʉʉsɨ yʉʉsi. Ɨrangʼeha kugirya abhaatʉ kwichʉrɨra Mungu na bhanagɨ, chɨmbu yaakʉrirɨ kwa niimwɨ kwɨma urusikʉ rʉnʉ mwigwirɨ igʉrʉ wʉ ʉrʉbhangʉ rwa Mungu, no okomenya amaheene igʉrʉ wɨ ɨbhɨgʉngi bhyazɨ.  
\v 7 Mʉkɨɨga Ɨngʼana Ɨnzʉmu yiyo kurwa kwa Ɨpafura, ʉmʉkɨndichɨtʉ ʉmʉsɨɨgwa. Ewe, ne‑mohocha moheene wa Kiriisitʉ igʉrʉ waanyu.  
\v 8 Akatʉbhʉʉrɨra igʉrʉ wʉ ʉbhʉsɨɨgi bhwanyu bhʉnʉ mʉhɨɨrwɨ ne Ekoro Ɨndɨndu.\f + \fr 1:8 \fk Ekoro Ɨndɨndu\ft . Kʉmaragɨrɨra bhʉkʉngʼu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* 
\p  
\v 9 Igʉrʉ wa riyo, tʉkɨɨrɨ kutiga kʉbhasabhɨra, kwɨma urusikʉ rʉnʉ twigwirɨ amangʼana gaanyu. Tʉrasabha Mungu abhahɨ ʉbhʉmɨnyi bhwʉsi kʉganʉ akwenda, kubhwʉbhʉʉri bhwaru nʉ ʉbhʉmɨnyi bhʉnʉ bhukurwa kwe Ekoro Ɨndɨndu.  
\v 10 Neho mʉkʉtʉra kwikara chɨmbu Ʉmʉkʉrʉ Yɨɨsu akwenda, na kokora ganʉ gakomozomera kʉmangʼana gʉʉsi. Ɨbhu nɨmbu muriibhʉrɨ imisumʉ komeremo ɨmɨzʉmu, na moroongera komenya Mungu.  
\v 11 Mungu abhanajɨ kʉbhʉnaja bhwazɨ bhwu ukuruguurya, korereke mʉtʉrɨ kwigumirirya hamwɨmwɨ no obhozomerwa.  
\v 12 Mmbe, mʉbhʉʉrɨrɨ Bhaabha Mungu azʉmiryɨ, wʉnʉ abhanagiryɨ kobhona ɨgabhʉ na abharɨndu bhaazɨ mʉbhʉtɨmi bhu ubhwɨrʉ.  
\v 13 Atʉsabhwirɨ kurwa mʉbhʉtɨmi bhwi ikiirimya, atʉsaamiryɨ na kutusikirya mʉbhʉtɨmi bhu Umwana waazɨ\f + \fr 1:13 \fk Umwana waazɨ\ft . Kʉmaragɨrɨra bhʉkʉngʼu, rora ringʼana \ft \+it Umwana wa Mungu\+it* muKiniibhasa.\f* ʉmʉsɨɨgwa.  
\v 14 Kʉ kʉhɨtɨra Umwana waazɨ tʉsabhwirwɨ, kʉ kʉbha ʉbhʉbhɨ bhwɨtʉ bhʉbhɨɨrɨɨrwɨ. 
\s1 Umwana wa Mungu anʉ ʉbhʉnaja igʉrʉ wa bhyʉsi 
\q1  
\v 15 Ewe, ne‑kerenjo cha Mungu wʉnʉ atakororekana. 
\q1 Nɨ‑mʉtangi we ebhegero bhyʉsi, 
\q1  
\v 16 kʉ kʉbha ebhegero bhyʉsi bhɨkateemwa kʉhɨtɨra kwawɨ, 
\q1 bhɨnʉ bhiri mwisaarʉ na mʉʉsɨ, 
\q1 bhɨnʉ bhekororekana na bhɨnʉ bhɨtakororekana, 
\q1 bhʉ ʉbhʉnaja hamwɨ abhatɨmi, abhakʉrʉ hamwɨ bha amanaga. 
\q1 Bhyʉsi bhɨkateemwa kʉhɨtɨra ewe ni igʉrʉ waazɨ. 
\q1  
\v 17 Ewe aareho kwɨma hanʉ ebhegero bhyʉsi bhyarɨ bhɨkɨɨrɨ koteemwa, 
\q1 na kʉhɨtɨra ewe ebhegero bhyʉsi bhɨhaagwatana hamwɨmwɨ. 
\q1  
\v 18 Ewe newe umutwɨ gwʉ ʉmʉbhɨrɨ, neryo risengerero. 
\q1 Ewe newe ʉbhʉtangɨ, 
\q1 kʉ kʉbha akabha we embere kuryʉka mʉbhaku, 
\q1 korereke abhɨ ʉmʉkʉrʉ we ebhegero bhyʉsi. 
\q1  
\v 19 Nɨmbu ɨkazomera Mungu, 
\q1 ʉbhʉnaja bhwazɨ bhwʉsi bhʉbhɨ muMwana waazɨ. 
\q1  
\v 20 Na ɨkazomera Mungu, 
\q1 kʉnzɨra yu Umwana waazɨ, 
\q1 Mungu agwatɨɨnʼyɨ ebhegero bhyʉsi neewe, 
\q1 bhɨnʉ bhɨrɨ mʉʉsɨ mʉnʉ na mwisaarʉ. 
\q1 Akakorabhu kwa koreeta omorembe, 
\q1 kʉhɨtɨra amasaahɨ gu Umwana waazɨ 
\q1 ganʉ giitikirɨ kʉmʉsarabha. 
\p  
\v 21 Zisikʉ zinyuma, imwʉsi mwarɨ kore na Mungu. Mwarɨ bhabhisa bhaazɨ mumiisɨɨgi gaanyu kwa zeteemwa zaanyu zɨmbɨ. Nawe nangʉ Mungu abhagwatɨɨnʼyɨ neewe,  
\v 22 kʉnzɨra yu uruku rwu Umwana waazɨ. Akakorabhu korereke abhatʉʉrɨ mʉbhʉtangɨ bhwazɨ, bharɨndu mʉrɨ, bhanʉ bhataana isoro nʉʉrʉ kuririirirwa.  
\v 23 Nawe moreenderwa kongʼeha kwisirirya Ɨngʼana Ɨnzʉmu mʉrɨ bhwɨma na kʉbha na amanaga. Mʉtachurwa na kutiga ubhwisɨgi bhʉnʉ mwabhwɨnɨ hanʉ mwigwirɨ Ɨngʼana Ɨnzʉmu. Ɨngʼana yiyo irwazirwɨ kʉbhaatʉ bhʉʉsi bha kʉʉsɨ kʉnʉ, inyɨ Paaurʉ nɨbhɨɨrɨ omohocha waazɨ. 
\s1 Emeremo ja Paaurʉ mʉmasengerero 
\p  
\v 24 Nangʉ nɨrazomererwa ɨnyaakʉ yɨnʉ nekobhona igʉrʉ waanyu. Mʉmʉbhɨrɨ gwanɨ nɨragwatana nɨ ɨnyaakʉ ya Kiriisitʉ igʉrʉ wʉ ʉmʉbhɨrɨ gwazɨ, neryo risengerero.  
\v 25 Mungu antɨɨrɨ omohocha wa risengerero ryazɨ, korereke nɨbharwazɨrɨ bhwaheene ɨngʼana yaazɨ.  
\v 26 Ɨngʼana yiyo neyo imbisi yu ubhwɨndi bhwazɨ bhʉnʉ bhwarɨ bhubhisirwɨ kuzinyibhʉrʉ zʉʉsi kwɨma ɨkarɨ. Nawe nangwɨnʉ Mungu ahumburiirɨ abharɨndu bhaazɨ.\f + \fr 1:26 \xt Rora Abheefeeso 3:3‑6.\f* 
\v 27 Mungu akasɨɨga kʉbhahumburɨra ubhwɨrʉ ʉbhʉkʉrʉ bhwi imbisi yɨnʉ yanyaragɨɨnɨ kʉbhaatʉ bhanʉ bhatarɨ Abhayaahudi. Imbisi yiyo neyo yɨnʉ, Kiriisitʉ arɨ kʉbhaniimwɨ, ubhwisɨgi bhwu ubhwɨrʉ. 
\p  
\v 28 Kiriisitʉ newe tukurwaza ɨngʼana yaazɨ tʉrakanya na kwija abhaatʉ bhʉʉsi kubhwʉbhʉʉri bhwʉsi, korereke tʉtʉrɨ kʉbhareeta bhʉʉsi mʉbhʉtangɨ bhwa Mungu ɨnʉ bhanagirɨ kukugwatana na Kiriisitʉ.  
\v 29 Kubhwɨndi bhuyo inyɨ nɨrakora emeremo na kwikongʼeererya kwa amanaga makʉrʉ ga Kiriisitʉ ganʉ gakokora emeremo mʉmʉbhɨrɨ gwanɨ. 
\c 2  
\p  
\v 1 Nereenda momenye chɨmbu nekokora emeremo kumucha igʉrʉ waanyu, igʉrʉ wa abhaatʉ bha Raʉdikiya, ni igʉrʉ wa abhandɨ bhanʉ bhakɨɨrɨ kondora.  
\v 2 Nɨrakorabhu korereke mʉhaanwɨ umwʉyʉ na kugwatanibhwa mʉbhʉsɨɨgi. Nereenda mobhone amangʼɨɨni gʉʉsi ganʉ gakʉbhaha obhoheene. Neho mokomenya imbisi ya Mungu, ni‑Kiriisitʉ umwene.  
\v 3 Kwewe bhyibhisirɨ ibhibhumbɨkʉ bhyʉsi bhyʉ ʉbhʉmɨnyi nu ubhwʉbhʉʉri. 
\p  
\v 4 Nɨrabhabhʉʉrɨra amangʼana ganʉ, korereke ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉwʉʉsi ataaza abhakangiriryɨ kʉmangʼana gʉ ʉrʉrɨmɨ, nangabha nɨ‑mazʉmu bhʉkʉngʼu.  
\v 5 Nɨragambabhu, nangabha nɨtarɨ hamwɨmwɨ na niimwɨ kwʉ ʉmʉbhɨrɨ, nawe nɨrɨ hamwɨmwɨ na niimwɨ kokoro. Nɨrazomerwa korora ubhumwɨmwɨ bhwanyu nʉ ʉbhʉnagu bhwu ubhwisirirya bhwanyu kwa Kiriisitʉ. 
\s1 Ubhwikari ubhuhya bhwi Ikikiriisitʉ 
\p  
\v 6 Mmbe nangʉ, chɨmbu mwisiriiryɨ Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ kʉbha Ʉmʉkʉrʉ, mongʼehe kwikara ku kugwatana neewe.  
\v 7 Mʉbhɨ ni imiri mʉʉsi waazɨ, mʉbhɨ bhwɨma kwewe na mʉnagɨ mubhwisirirya chɨmbu mwijibhwɨ. Na mʉbhɨ abhaatʉ bhanʉ bhakukumya Mungu ibhaga ryʉsi. 
\p  
\v 8 Mwangarɨrɨ, mʉtaaza kurimiribhwa kumiija ga bhʉʉha na amakangirirya gʉ ʉrʉrɨmɨ, ku ukugwata amangʼana ga bhaatʉ. Amiija gayo gariisega isimʉka yɨnʉ ɨkʉkangata ɨɨsɨ\f + \fr 2:8 \fk Isimʉka yɨnʉ ɨkʉkangata ɨɨsɨ\ft , ʉbhʉgaruri ʉbhʉndɨ bhʉratʉra kʉbha, \fqa amasambwa ganʉ gakʉkangata ɨɨsɨ. \ft Nɨmbu ɨrɨ nʉ ʉrʉkɨrɨrɨ \xt 2:20\ft .\f* na ɨtarɨ ya Kiriisitʉ,  
\v 9 kʉ kʉbha ʉbhʉnaja bhwʉsi bhwa Mungu bhʉrɨ mʉmʉbhɨrɨ gwa Kiriisitʉ.  
\v 10 Na niimwɨ mʉhɨɨrwɨ ʉbhʉhʉru bhwʉsi ku kugwatana na Kiriisitʉ. Ewe newe ari igʉrʉ wa amasambwa, abhatɨmi na abhakʉrʉ bhʉʉsi kowereero yɨnʉ ɨtakororekana.  
\v 11 Hanʉ mwagwatɨɨnɨ na Kiriisitʉ, mʉkatiga ʉbhʉbhɨ kwa kʉsaarwa\f + \fr 2:11 \fk Kʉsaarwa\ft . Kʉmaragɨrɨra bhʉkʉngʼu, rora ringʼana \ft \+it ʉkʉsaara\+it* muKiniibhasa.\f* na Kiriisitʉ. Mʉtaasaarirwɨ kwa amabhoko ga abhaatʉ, nawe kʉnzɨra yaazɨ umwene.  
\v 12 Hanʉ mwʉjirwɨ amabhɨ, mʉkakwa, mʉkabhiikwa hamwɨmwɨ na Kiriisitʉ. Na mʉkaryʉka hamwɨmwɨ nawe, ku ukwisirirya zinguru za Mungu wʉnʉ aamuryurirɨ kurwa mʉbhaku. 
\p  
\v 13 Na niimwɨ mwarɨ abhaku igʉrʉ wʉ ʉbhʉbhɨ bhwanyu, na mʉtaasaarirwɨ kusimʉka yʉ ʉbhʉbhɨ bhwanyu. Nawe Mungu abhahɨɨrɨ ʉbhʉhʉru hamwɨmwɨ na Kiriisitʉ na atʉbhɨɨrɨɨrɨ ʉbhʉbhɨ bhwɨtʉ bhwʉsi.  
\v 14 Aturihiirɨ isiirɨ yʉ ʉbhʉbhɨ bhwɨtʉ kʉnzɨra ya Yɨɨsu kutukwɨra kʉmʉsarabha. Akahuta ɨnyarʉbha yɨnʉ yatʉgambirɨ ni imigirʉ jaku, akayiruushaho kwa koyetemerera kʉmʉsarabha.  
\v 15 Kʉnzɨra yʉ ʉmʉsarabha, Mungu akabharuusha ʉbhʉnaja bhwa abhatɨmi na abhakʉrʉ bhʉʉsi kowereero yɨnʉ ɨtakororekana, arabhakangata habhwɨrʉ kubhuhiza bhwazɨ kwa bhozomerwa. 
\p  
\v 16 Mmbe, ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉwʉʉsi atabhatɨnɨra igʉrʉ wi ibhyakurya, hamwɨ bhyukunywa, hamwɨ isigukuru yɨ ɨnyangi, hamwɨ isigukuru yʉ ʉkʉtaazwa ku umwɨri, hamwɨ urusikʉ rwʉ ʉbhʉtʉʉrʉ.\f + \fr 2:16 \fk Urusikʉ rwʉ ʉbhʉtʉʉrʉ\ft . Kʉmaragɨrɨra bhʉkʉngʼu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* 
\v 17 Gayo gʉʉsi ni‑kikiriiri cha amangʼana ganʉ gakuuza. Nawe amangʼana ageene gararorekana kwa Kiriisitʉ umwene.  
\v 18 Mutiisirirya kutinirwa na mʉʉtʉ wʉwʉʉsi wʉnʉ akwikumya amagenderero gaazɨ gu ukwiyicha, na kokosengera bhamaraika.\f + \fr 2:18 \fk Bhamaraika\ft . Kʉmaragɨrɨra bhʉkʉngʼu, rora ringʼana \ft \+it maraika\+it* muKiniibhasa.\f* Mʉtabhiisirirya bhataaza kʉbharuusha ʉmʉbhanʉ gwanyu gwa kemerano. Abhaatʉ bhayo bhariiyʉnga, kʉ kʉbha bharabhuga bharʉʉzɨ amangʼana gayo mʉbhʉrʉri. Nawe amaheene, bhagɨɨgɨhirɨ kumiisɨɨgi ga amakangirirya gaabhʉ gɨ ɨɨsɨ.  
\v 19 Na bhiiyahwirɨ na Kiriisitʉ wʉnʉ akʉkangata risengerero, aarɨ umutwɨ gwʉ ʉmʉbhɨrɨ gwazɨ. Kiriisitʉ newe akuriisha na kugwatanʼya hamwɨmwɨ ibhiimʉ ni imigiha jʉsi. Ʉmʉbhɨrɨ gwazɨ gwʉsi gʉrakʉra bhwaheene chɨmbu Mungu akwenda. 
\p  
\v 20 Mʉkakwa hamwɨmwɨ na Kiriisitʉ, na kutiga amiija gayo gakwisega isimʉka yɨnʉ ɨkʉkangata ɨɨsɨ yɨnʉ. Kwakɨ muriitʉʉra iyaasɨ wa amaswaja gaabhʉ gɨ ɨɨsɨ, ncha abhiikari bha kʉʉsɨ?  
\v 21 “Mʉtagwata kɨnʉ! Mʉtasama kiyo! Mʉtakunʼyaku kirya!”  
\v 22 Gayo gʉʉsi ni‑maragɨrɨra na amiija ga abhaatʉ igʉrʉ we ebhegero bhɨnʉ bhɨkʉsarɨka hanʉ bhɨkʉmara kohocherwa kwibhaga isuuhu.  
\v 23 Nɨ‑maheene, bhanʉ bhakutuna imigirʉ giyo bhararorekana bhanu ubhwʉbhʉʉri. Bharatuna ʉbhʉsɨngɨri\f + \fr 2:23 \fk Ʉbhʉsɨngɨri\ft . Kʉmaragɨrɨra bhʉkʉngʼu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* bhʉnʉ bhiitɨɨrɨɨrɨ abheene, ukwiyicha kwɨ ɨkɨbhɨɨhi nʉ ʉkʉkangata ʉmʉbhɨrɨ kwa bhʉhaari. Nawe imigirʉ giyo gɨtakʉtʉra korecha umwʉyʉ ʉmʉbhɨ gwʉ ʉmʉbhɨrɨ. 
\c 3  
\p  
\v 1 Nangʉ, kʉ kʉbha muryukirɨ hamwɨmwɨ na Kiriisitʉ, momohye amangʼana ga mwisaarʉ ɨnʉ Kiriisitʉ ikɨɨrɨ, ʉrʉbhaara rwu ubhuryʉ rwa Mungu.  
\v 2 Mwiseege amangʼana ganʉ gari mwisaarʉ, mutiiseega ganʉ garɨ kʉʉsɨ,  
\v 3 kʉ kʉbha mʉkakwa nʉ ʉbhʉhʉru bhwanyu bhubhisirwɨ hamwɨmwɨ na Kiriisitʉ kwa Mungu,  
\v 4 ewe newe ʉbhʉhʉru bhwanyu. Hanʉ arerorekanɨ, neho na niimwɨ mʉraarorekanɨ hamwɨmwɨ nawe mubhwɨrʉ bhwazɨ. 
\p  
\v 5 Mmbe, mutigɨ amangʼana gʉʉsi ga kʉʉsɨ ganʉ garɨ kʉbhaniimwɨ, ɨtaarʉ, umwʉyʉ ʉmʉbhɨ, amiisɨɨgi amabhɨ, nu umwʉyʉ gwe ebhegero. Kʉbha nu umwʉyʉ gwe ebhegero kutuubhɨɨnɨ no okosengera amasambwa.  
\v 6 Amangʼana gayo, nego gakokora Mungu atɨnɨrɨ abhaatʉ bhanʉ bhatakumwigwa.\f + \fr 3:6 \ft Zibhibhuriya ɨzɨndɨ zɨtaana amangʼana ganʉ, \fqa abhaatʉ bhanʉ bhatakumwigwa. \xt Rora Abheefeeso 5:6.\f* 
\v 7 Ɨkarɨ, imwʉsi mwarɨ muriikara kʉrɨngʼaana na amangʼana gayo, hanʉ mwarɨ kugwatana na abhaatʉ ncha bhayo.  
\v 8 Nawe nangʉ mutigɨ amangʼana gayo gʉʉsi, hamwɨmwɨ nʉ ʉbhʉrʉrʉ, ubhwigatani, ʉbhʉbhɨ, amatuki na ganʉ gatakwenderwa muminywa janyu.  
\v 9 Mutiibhʉʉrɨra ʉrʉrɨmɨ, kʉ kʉbha mutigirɨ ubhwikari bhwɨ ɨkarɨ hamwɨmwɨ na amahocha gaaku,  
\v 10 na mwibhʉhirɨ obhoronge ubhuhya. Mungu umwene akateema obhoronge bhuyo, na arangʼeha kokora bhutuubhanɨ bhʉkʉngʼu neewe, korereke mʉtʉrɨ komomenya bhwaheene.  
\v 11 Hanʉ bhʉtareeho bhwahʉkani gatɨ wʉ Ʉmʉyaahudi na wʉnʉ atarɨ Ʉmʉyaahudi, wʉnʉ asaarirwɨ na wʉnʉ atasaarirwɨ, umugini hamwɨ umushɨnzi, mbʉʉsa nu umwiyagaaruri. Nawe Kiriisitʉ newe gʉʉsi kwa gʉʉsi, ewe arɨ kʉbhaniimwɨ. 
\p  
\v 12 Nangʉ, kʉ kʉbha imwɨ mʉbhɨɨrɨ abharobhorwa bha Mungu, na abharɨndu abhasɨɨgwa, mʉbhɨ nu umwʉyʉ gwɨ ɨbhɨgʉngi, ʉbhʉzʉmu, ubhusuuku, ʉbhʉnyʉʉhu nu ubhwigumirirya.  
\v 13 Arɨɨbhɨ wʉmwɨ waanyu ana ringʼana nʉ ʉmʉkɨndichazɨ, mwigege na kwibheerera. Moreenderwa kwibheerera chɨmbu Ʉmʉkʉrʉ aabhabhɨɨrɨɨrɨ.  
\v 14 Kʉkɨra gayo gʉʉsi mʉsɨɨganɨ, kʉ kʉbha ʉbhʉsɨɨgi nebhwe bhukugwatanʼya bhʉʉsi mubhumwɨmwɨ bhʉnʉ bhʉnagirɨ.  
\v 15 Omorembe gwa Kiriisitʉ gʉkangatɨ mumyʉyʉ janyu, kʉ kʉbha negwe mubhirikiriirwɨ kʉmʉbhɨrɨ gʉmwɨ. Na mʉbhɨ mʉrakumya Mungu.  
\v 16 Ringʼana rya Kiriisitʉ ryikarɨ kwa bhwaru kʉbhaniimwɨ, ɨnʉ muriiyija na kwiyangirija kubhwʉbhʉʉri bhwʉsi. Mwɨmbɨrɨ Mungu kumyʉyʉ janyu na kumukumya, kwa zabhuri, amɨɨmbʉ na zɨtɨnzi za mokoro. 
\p  
\v 17 Gʉgʉʉsi ganʉ mʉkʉgamba hamwɨ kokora, mokore kuriina ryʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ Yɨɨsu, mʉrabhʉʉrɨra Bhaabha Mungu azʉmiryɨ kʉhɨtɨra kwawɨ. 
\s1 Ubhwikari ʉbhʉzʉmu muzinyumba za Abhakiriisitʉ 
\p  
\v 18 Abhakari imwɨ, mʉsʉʉkɨ abhasubhɨ bhaanyu, chɨmbu ikwenderwa kʉbhaatʉ bhanʉ bhakwisirirya Ʉmʉkʉrʉ Yɨɨsu.  
\v 19 Na niimwɨ abhasubhɨ, mʉsɨɨgɨ abhakari bhaanyu, mʉtabha bhahaari kwebho.  
\v 20 Na niimwɨ abhaana, mʉsʉʉkɨ abhiibhuri bhaanyu kʉmangʼana gʉʉsi, kʉ kʉbha okokorabhu kʉrazomera Ʉmʉkʉrʉ Yɨɨsu.  
\v 21 Na niimwɨ bha bhaabha, moteendeerya abhaana bhaanyu, korereke bhataaza kukwa imyʉyʉ.  
\v 22 Na niimwɨ bhambʉʉsa, mʉsʉʉkɨ abhakʉrʉ bhaanyu komeremo jʉsi. Mokorebhu, ɨtarɨ hanʉ bhakʉbharora korereke mwikombe kwabhʉ, nawe mʉbhasʉʉkɨ ribhaga ryʉsi kʉbhʉgʉrʉrʉku bhu umwʉyʉ, kʉ kʉbha mʉrasengera Ʉmʉkʉrʉ Yɨɨsu.  
\v 23 Ryʉryʉsi rɨnʉ mʉrakora, mokore kumwʉyʉ, chɨmbu mokohokerya Ʉmʉkʉrʉ, ɨtarɨ abhaatʉ.  
\v 24 Muhiitɨ kʉbha arabhaha ʉmʉbhanʉ gwɨ ɨgabhʉ. Kwɨbhu mohokerye Ʉmʉkʉrʉ Kiriisitʉ.  
\v 25 Nawe wʉwʉʉsi wʉnʉ akokora amabhɨ arasʉngʼaana kʉrɨngʼaana nʉ ʉbhʉbhɨ bhwazɨ, kʉ kʉbha Ʉmʉkʉrʉ ataana kɨmbʉrʉʉri. 
\c 4  
\m  
\v 1 Na niimwɨ abhakʉrʉ, mʉbhɨ mʉrakorera bhambʉʉsa bhaanyu ge eheene na ganʉ bhakwenderwa. Muhiitɨ kʉbha imwʉsi mʉnawɨ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ mwisaarʉ. 
\s1 Amaswaja na amasabhi ga Paaurʉ 
\p  
\v 2 Mʉbhɨ mʉrasabha sikʉ zʉʉsi, mʉratengeeza mʉmasabhi na kʉbhʉʉrɨra Mungu azʉmiryɨ.  
\v 3 Mʉtʉsabhɨrɨ na niitwɨ korereke Mungu atwigʉrɨrɨ ɨnzɨra ya ringʼana ryazɨ, turwazɨ Ɨngʼana ya Kiriisitʉ yɨnʉ yaarɨ ibhisirwɨ. Na niinyɨ nɨbhʉhirwɨ igʉrʉ wu ukwerekeererya ɨngʼana yiyo.  
\v 4 Mʉbhɨ mʉrasabha Mungu nɨbhɨ na amanaga gu ukwerekeererya habhwɨrʉ ɨngʼana yiyo chɨmbu nikwenderwa kʉgamba. 
\p  
\v 5 Mʉbhɨ nu ubhwʉbhʉʉri mubhwigwani bhwanyu na abhaatʉ bhanʉ bhakɨɨrɨ kwisirirya Yɨɨsu. Mohokerye umweya guyo bhwaheene.  
\v 6 Amangʼana gaanyu gabhɨ mazʉmu na masambaruku, korereke momenye chɨmbu mukwenderwa kʉgarukirya abhaatʉ bhʉʉsi. 
\s1 Amangʼana gʉ ʉkʉraga 
\p  
\v 7 Tikikʉ umwisirirya ʉmʉsɨɨgwa no omohocha ʉmʉkɨndichɨtʉ omoronge wʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ, arabhaha amangʼana gaanɨ gʉʉsi.  
\v 8 Nimutumirɨ kwa niimwɨ korereke momenye amangʼana gɨɨtʉ na kʉbhaha umwʉyʉ.  
\v 9 Araaza hamwɨmwɨ na Ʉnɨsimʉ, umwisirirya ʉmʉkɨndichɨtʉ ʉmʉsɨɨgwa no omoheene, nɨ‑mʉʉtʉ wu uwaanyu. Bhayo bharabhaha amangʼana gʉʉsi ganʉ gakokorwa ɨwɨɨtʉ hanʉ. 
\p  
\v 10 Arisitʉʉrikʉ, wʉnʉ abhʉhirwɨ hamwɨmwɨ na niinyɨ, arabhakeerya. Maaroko umwabhʉ Bharinaabha, wʉnʉ mʉsʉngʼaanirɨ ameerekenʼyʉ igʉrʉ waazɨ, wʉʉsi arabhakeerya. Araahikɨ, mumuginihyɨ bhwaheene.  
\v 11 Na Yɨɨsu, wʉnʉ akubhirikirwa Yuusitʉ, arabhakeerya. MʉBhayaahudi bhanʉ bhiisiriiryɨ Kiriisitʉ, bhanʉ nebho abheene bhakokora emeremo igʉrʉ wʉ ʉbhʉtɨmi bhwa Mungu hamwɨmwɨ na niinyɨ, na bhangʼɨɨrɨ umwʉyʉ bhʉkʉngʼu.  
\v 12 Ɨpafura, ʉmʉʉtʉ wɨ ɨwaanyu, omohocha wa Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ, arabhakeerya. Sikʉ zʉʉsi arakora umucha kʉbhasabhɨra korereke mʉtʉrɨ kwimɨɨrɨra bhwɨma, mokongʼe na mʉnajɨ amangʼana gʉʉsi ganʉ Mungu akwenda.  
\v 13 Nɨramomenyeekererya kʉbha, arakora emeremo ku umucha igʉrʉ waanyu na kʉbhaatʉ bha zɨmbɨri za Raʉdikiya na Hiyɨrapʉri.  
\v 14 Ruuka ʉmʉgabhʉ wɨɨtʉ ʉmʉsɨɨgwa, na Deema, bharabhakeerya.  
\v 15 Imwɨ, mʉbhakeerye abhiisirirya abhakɨndichɨtʉ bha Raʉdikiya. Na mokeerye Nimufa, na abhaatʉ bha risengerero rɨnʉ riri munyumba yaazɨ. 
\p  
\v 16 Hanʉ mʉraamarɨ kosoma ɨnyarʉbha yɨnʉ, muyihichɨ kwa abhaatʉ bha risengerero rya Raʉdikiya, korereke bhʉʉsi bhayesome. Na niimwɨ momohye ɨnzɨra yo okobhona na kosoma ɨnyarʉbha yɨnʉ nabhatumiirɨ.  
\v 17 Mʉbhʉʉrɨrɨ Arikipʉ, amarɨ bhwaheene emeremo gɨnʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ amʉhɨɨrɨ. 
\p  
\v 18 Inyɨ Paaurʉ nɨraandɨka amakeerenʼya ganʉ kokobhoko kwanɨ inyimwene. Muhiitɨ kʉbha nɨrɨ mokebhoho. Ɨbhɨgʉngi bhya Mungu bhɨbhɨ hamwɨmwɨ na niimwɨ.